# MVVM Architecture

- ViewModel: @Observable @MainActor final class; state properties, action methods
- Service protocol in domain; implementation in data
- Constructor injection; @Environment for cross-cutting
- Errors: AppError enum; map at data boundary; surface in ViewModel error state
- SwiftUI .alert for error presentation
